      section
        h1#drag Drag
        h2 Drag coefficient
        p The drag coefficient is the sum of the profile drag and the induced drag, with #[var K] being a constant depending on the wing planform shape.
        p \[ C_D = C_{D_0} + C_{D_i} = C_{D_0} + \frac{K}{\pi A}C_L^2 \]

        h2 Minimum drag speed
        p \[ V_{MD} = \left(\frac{2W}{\rho S}\right)^\frac{1}{2} \left(\frac{K}{\pi A C_{D_0}}\right)^\frac{1}{4} \]

        h2 Minimum drag
        p \[ D_{min} = 2W \left(\frac{K C_{D_0}}{\pi A}\right)^\frac{1}{2} \]



